{"tid":1631892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佢要扮你邊有得避 咪撚ON9乜撚都仆去認投","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:56.000Z","uid":73419,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad7cabd2345307ff7bf38d7dc0def07f2e1faf7","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88ff846e6af4602de6b5b9a839976a71962f1ce","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f376e862c66ea63720a9ab197d6ba74e52dcc7e","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915259bf5189d8643865ae4c11dc1ab59c305327","tid":1631892,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:47.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布！聽日係全民文宣日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631729</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c26e379c3b9463b319c5a5bee98d54af2bbf53ca","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffa437e9a2b74c620014409fad7942a2a2224eb","tid":1631892,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:00.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a8576d267d70f90331caeaab4aec7c226e7c6123","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e5049b18d51f4ed44d8c1116739d2086a40f9a","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fd7d781b53c279a124a79e44368f28652a4b9b","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4cc3a06836d3017982049f4aa2e28e6e8f385b","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448266fd14c8831b66245e02ea6e1aa9cee3f2da","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f1f2ea41fc31a8565e29138c4b1de673151189","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ffb373a9f81373f962bcfa6ee9a8666172bc4e","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9952c8af64c7e202d0eb11976572bac0c208785e","tid":1631892,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"支那五毛出盡力想手足認頭"},{"pid":"a12d9410c57505c7fe8238d02a965bbb1e04280a","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0fbeaeb6a2a646d252618404758a60d4c5e5f542","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a971a6fe228d5430a4557a63c388b036d334e08","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc5f0714ade18f0bbf3e33fb5297d664cccc072","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53e1e4d24f6772ccfd23dd90380f22d62f5c747","tid":1631892,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}